I was alittle hesitant to try this recipe, since every other recipe for rack of lamb tells you to brown the meat first and then finish it in the oven. But I followed the recipe exactly, and it came out great! Meat was a perfect "medium-rare", and the rosemary-pesto formed a delicious crust. Don't think about trying this recipe, just try it!!

